quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  11,24,"Misal feddeeji Й—in Й—in: ko wano bunЙ—o e faaЙ—uЙ—o, e yi'oowo e nanoowo. E Й“ee Й—oo Й—iЙ—i fotay e misal? E on waajitotaako"
  11,25,"GomЙ—ii Men Nulirii Nuuhu e yimЙ“e makko Й“en: \"Min wonannde on ko mi jertinoowo Й“annginЙ—o"
  11,26,wonnde wata on rewu si wanah Alla. Min miЙ—o hulani on lepte Г±alaande musuunde
  11,27,"Mbatu Й“en yedduЙ“e e yimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'i: Men yi'aali ma si wanah ko a Й“anndinke sifa amen, men yi'aali kadi Й“en jokkuЙ“e ma si wo- naa jaasuЙ“e amen faaЙ—uЙ“e feere, men yi'anaali on e amen Й“ural. Worin meЙ—en sikki ko on fenooЙ“e"
  11,28,"O maaki: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, yeetee lam si tawii miЙ—o e Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi am, O yeЙ—ii lam yurmeende (Annabaaku) immorde ka Makko, Й—um wumna e mooЙ—on, e menm baaw- nay on nde hara ko on aГ±uЙ“e nde"
  11,29,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, mi lanndaaki on jawdi e Й—um. NjoЙ“di am wonaali si wanah ka Alla. Min mi wonaali raЙ—otooЙ—o Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, kamЙ“e ko Й“e hawroyooЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Ko woni tun, min mi yi'ii on yimЙ“e majjuЙ“e"
  11,30,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, ko hommbo walloytammi ka Alla si mi raЙ—ike Й“e? E on waajitotaako"
  11,31,"Mi wi'antah on miЙ—o mari ngaluujii Alla, mi annah kadi ko wirnii, mi wi'ataa wonnde ko mi malayko, mi wi'antaa Й“en Й“e gite mon Й—en yawi, Alla okkoytaa-Й“e moЖґЖґere; ko Alla Й“uri anndude ko woni e wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e. Min ontuma [si mi waЙ—ii Й—um], haray ko mi jeyaaЙ—o e tooГ±uЙ“e Й“en"
  11,32,"ЖЃe wi'i: \"Ko an yo Nuuhu, gomЙ—ii a wenjidii e amen, a Й—uЙ—Й—inii yeddondiral ngal e amen. Addan men kon ko fodu-Й—aa men, si a laatike jeyaaЙ—o e goonguЙ“e Й“en"
  11,33,"O maaki: \"Anndee ko Alla addanta on Й—e -si O muuyii- on wonaali laawotooЙ“e"
  11,34,"LaaЙ“al-reedu am nafatah on, si mi faandike laaЙ“angol on, si tawii Alla no faandii bewnugol on (majjina). Ko Kanko woni Joomi mon, ko ka Makko woni ruttorde mon"
  11,35,"Si ko woni, Й“e wi'ay : O fefidi-nde. Maaku: \"Si mi fefindi nde, haray bonnere am nden no fawii lam. Min no ko mi daЙ—ndiiЙ—o ko bonnoton kon"
  11,36,"Wahayinaa e Nuuhu wonnde : \"GomЙ—intah e yimЙ“e maa Й“en si wanaa Й“en gomЙ—innooЙ“e. Wata a suno e ko Й“e gollaynoo"
  11,37,"MoЖґЖґin laana kan e ndeenka Amen e yamiroore Amen. Wata a yewtidoy e am fii Й“en tooГ±uЙ“e, kamЙ“e ko Й“e yoolotooЙ“e. @Corrected"
  11,38,"Himo moЖґЖґina laana kan. Tuma kala nde dental hoorewal rewi ka o moЖґЖґinta ton, Й“e jalkita mo. O maaki: \"Si on jalkitii men, menen kadi men jalkitoyay on wano jalkitirton [men non]"
  11,39,"Aray nde annduЙ—on ko hommbo lepte hoynayЙ—e aroyat e muuЙ—um, lepte duumiiЙ—e jippoo e makko"
  11,40,"Haa si yamiroore Amen nden aroyii, huЙ“Й“inirЙ—e Й—en fati, Men daali: \"Ronndo e makka kala nooneeji Й—iЙ—i resindirayЙ—i e Й“eynguure maa nden -si wanaa Й“en konngol lepte ngol adii e mu'un- e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e\". GomЙ—inaano wonndude e makko si wonah seeЙ—aaЙ“e"